data.description: Please come see this charming 2 bedroom 1 1/2 bath Cape cod home that is move in ready.  It has a large eat in kitchen with and all the appliances are included. This home is off Jefferson and the Nautical Mile and has a lovely side yard off the family room. Backyard is nice and spacious for entertaining.  New hot water tank 2023. Owner had crawl space encapsulation and structural work done 2022. There is a warranty that will be transfer to the new owner.
